name: Agross
summary: Agross is a survival resource management game . You play the role of a farmer.

name: DDRMax2: Dance Dance Revolution
summary: The dance floor kicks into overdrive with DDRMAX2 Dance Dance Revolution. It is the latest installment of the highly anticipated DDR series and takes the revolution to the masses! Players can customize their own dance steps and workout in an innovative Exercise Mode. DDR is packed with a smash-hit lineup of all-new exclusive songs  licensed music and dance hits. There are cool contemporary game modes and brand new graphical interfaces featuring music videos that will keep everybody movin  and groovin  to the pulsating beats. DDR Max 2 also includes links to previous games for special features.

name: Space station - build your own ISS
Bubble Whirl Shooter
summary: Shoot bubbles and match colors to pop your way up to victory in this bubble shooting adventure  win magic keys to unlock more secret colorful bubble world  it’s time to enjoy the endless bubble shooting fun!

name: Stickman and the Sword of Legends
summary: Stickman needs to get the Sword of Legends to be able to leave his planet that is about to explode.

name: All Alone
summary: A missing father  a mysterious murder  paintings depicting missing children. Horror game in which the protagonist  who has lost his memory  is forced to get to a horrific truth. Who in the world are you?

name: Corallo
summary: Corallo is a Yume Nikki fangame. The main focus is exploring  dreams  and collecting  effects   which can be purely cosmetic or make the character perform certain actions.  Corallo focuses on Maya  a young woman stuck on a wheelchair and locked in a room. She can only stare at the ocean in front of her window and daydream. By interacting with her mind  the player can learn more about her and her past  and what lead her to be stuck in her current room.

name: The Long Reach

platforms.name: Linux
platforms.summary: Linux is a free and open-source (FOSS/FLOSS) Operating System. In a more precise and complex definition, Linux is an open-source OS kernel on which a large variety of Operating Systems (known as Linux distributions) are built.

platforms.name: PlayStation 4
platforms.summary: The PlayStation 4 system opens the door to an incredible journey through immersive new gaming worlds and a deeply connected gaming community. PS4 puts gamers first with an astounding launch line-up and over 180 games in development. Play amazing top-tier blockbusters and innovative indie hits on PS4. Developer inspired, gamer focused.

platforms.name: Xbox One
platforms.summary: Welcome to a new generation of games and entertainment. Where games push the boundaries of realism. And television obeys your every command. Where listening to music while playing a game is a snap. And you can jump from TV to movies to music to a game in an instant. Where your experience is custom tailored to you. And the entertainment you love is all in one place. Welcome to the all-in-one, Xbox One

summary: At its heart The Long Reach is an adventure game. Closer inspection also reveals it s a thrilling horror story  flavoured with sci-fi ideology  psychological context and a skeptical view on the human psyche.

name: Pet Puzzle
summary: Pet Puzzle is a relaxing and leisurely three-in-a-row game.

name: Ganbare Goemon: Mononoke Sugoroku
summary: A compilation of the first two Super Famicom Goemon games.

name: Tiger Tank 59 I: A-Gun MP095
summary: Tiger Tank 59  is a top-down shooting game. Players need to control their tanks  through the enemy lines  break the enemy base  or defeat the enemy tanks. This DLC contains the Map No.491-495.

name: Escape Jump
summary: Escape Jump is a precision platformer where you and your funny companion jump and fall  rage-quit and fall  flip your table  destroy your computer  put it back together and then you fall.

name: Meat & Greed
summary: In the atmospheric puzzle-platformer Meat & Greed  you will experience the horrors of a slaughterhouse from the perspective of different animals. Solve riddles and collaborate with other animals to try and escape this ill-fated factory.

name: Chicku
summary: Chicku is a nail bitingly hard platformer in which the player has to escape the evil Barrington farm. You ll be forced to dodge saws  spikes and many other deadly traps in order to save your brethren and rise against the evil Dr. Barrington.

name: Shadow Wolf Mysteries: Cursed Wedding - Collector's Edition
summary: After being called to Paris  you find yourself in the middle of a shocking mystery involving an ancient werewolf hungry for revenge.

name: Fantasy Life i: The Girl Who Steals Time
storyline: A new chapter of Fantasy Life that transcends time!  Begin a fantastic life on a ruined island  and embark on a great adventure into the past! Gather friends  craft  and build your own city!
summary: Fantasy Life i: The Girl Who Steals Time is an RPG life-sim game and the long-awaited sequel to the 3DS classic Fantasy Life. This game will expand on what the original did  blending simulation with traditional action RPG combat mechanics.

name: Damned Cold
summary: Damned Cold is a twin-stick shooter where you play as a prisoner of war trying to escape their captors through killing cold in a reactive diesel-punk world.

name: Super Kirby Clash
storyline: Long  long ago  in a faraway realm  there was a beautiful  peaceful land called the Dream Kingdom. One surprising day  Hornhead went on a rampage across the Seaside. And so it came to pass that Team Kirby set off on an adventure to restore peace to the kingdom...
summary: Power through bosses on a team of four!  To defeat bosses this wicked  it’ll take a whole team of Kirbys! In this free-to-start multiplayer action game  you can choose from four unique Roles and join up to three other players to take down tough bosses. Puff up your power by crafting weapons and spending materials at the shop to receive even MORE weapons  not to mention armor and items. Pass a Joy-Con controller to a friend to play locally  and if you have a Nintendo Switch Online membership  you can even play online!  Are you a Sword Hero? Hammer Lord? Beam Mage? Or Doctor Healmore?! No matter what  each mighty role offers up a unique way to play. Story Quest lets players team-up locally by sharing Joy-Con controllers  while Party Quest enables users to play together on one system  via local wireless  or online. Plus  tapping compatible amiibo figures/accessories will earn you extra fragments to help craft new gear! Are you ready? For Kirby  the answer is always fight and flight.
